# =====================================================================
# AMR Sentinel — .gitignore
# Bulletproof exclusion of submission materials, internal docs, secrets,
# generated data, and standard build/IDE artifacts.
# =====================================================================

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Vivli submission materials and internal process notes — NEVER commit
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
vivli_submission/
tasks/
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE-*.md
claude.md
*draft*
*Draft*
*DRAFT*
reply_drafts.md
outreach_*.md
outreach_*.csv
Replies.txt
preregistration*.md
EOI*.md
framework_brief*.md
render_pdfs.ps1
*.pdf
osf_deposit_checklist.md
execution_priorities.md

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Secrets and local configuration
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.local
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets/
.secrets/
**/credentials.json
**/service-account*.json

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
